Cincinnati who was in the helicopter, was treated and released for
minor injuries at Mercy Hospital, Katt said.
   The helicopter pilot was not hurt, the officer said.
   The plane was attempting to carry the banner over Riverfront
Stadium for a game between the Cincinnati Bengals and the Houston
Oilers. Katt said he did not know the size of the banner.
